These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, swisher, bongani, bluemaster
City: berlin, miami, hamburg, edinburgh
1. the swisher-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the person traveling to miami##2
2. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
3. the swisher-smoker is somewhere between the bluemaster-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##7
4. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar   | bongani | bluemaster       | swisher | bolivar        |
| City      | hamburg  | miami | edinburgh        | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, thai, malaysian, polish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, disaster, time-travel, romance
1. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the malaysian##7
2. the polish is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
3. the polish is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
4. the thai is on the left of the polish##1
5. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching disaster movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Nationality     | malaysian | thai       | polish         | chinese     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | romance | time-travel | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, ferret, snake, dog
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, firefighter, architect, nurse
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the nurse is somewhere between the firefighter and the entrepreneur##7
3. the architect is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the entrepreneur is somewhere between the nurse and the owner of the ferret##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Pet   | ferret | dog | snake | frog  |
| Job   | architect | entrepreneur  | nurse   | firefighter |

