.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, crime, romance, mystery
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, social-worker, videographer, designer
1. the designer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the social-worker and the person watching mystery movies##7
3. the person watching romance movies is the designer##1
4. the videographer is on the left of the designer##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | western | mystery       | romance |
| Job   | social-worker      | firefighter   | videographer | designer  |

