.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, rock, jazz
City: rome, marseilles, edinburgh, colone
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the fan electronic##3
2. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
3. the fan disco is on the right of the fan rock##1
4. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the fan electronic and the fan disco##7
5. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
7. the fan electronic is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan disco is on the left or right of the fan rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | rock | disco   | jazz | electronic |
| City   | rome      | marseilles | colone      | edinburgh |

