.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, romance, martial-arts, sports
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, billiard, backgammon
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing billiard is the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person playing snooker##7
7. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | romance | superhero      | martial-arts | sports     |
| Game   | poker    | backgammon | snooker   | billiard |

