.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, western, musical
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, march, june
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching western movies##7
5. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | musical    | adventure   | thriller | western  |
| Birthday   | december | march | june    | october |

