The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, electronic, pop, r&b
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, november, july
1. the fan electronic is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
3. the fan r&b is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the fan pop is somewhere between the fan r&b and the fan house##7
5. the fan electronic is on the left of the fan house##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | pop | electronic | house |
| Birthday           | november   | july    | may       | february  |

