2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person who growsbellflower and the person playing backgammon##7
6. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Game           | whist | canasta | monopoly | backgammon |
| Flower   | bellflower         | poppy      | dahlia | aconite            |

