.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, chinese, thai, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, swimming, handball
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the malaysian is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the thai##1
4. the thai is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6
5. the thai is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the thai##7
7. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality       | malaysian | dutch | chinese | thai |
| Sport   | rowing   | handball      | water-polo        | swimming  |

