.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, motorbike, helicopter
There 4 different types of food: mango, carrot, garlic, potato
1. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
2. the person eating potato is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person eating garlic##7
3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
4. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
7. the person driving the subway is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Transport      | snowmobile   | motorbike | subway | helicopter   |
| Food   | mango | garlic   | potato | carrot |

