4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, snooker, billiard
1. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the person playing billiard##7
2. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the ferret is not the person playing billiard##6
5. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person playing snooker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Pet   | fish | frog     | dog     | ferret |
| Game     | billiard | snooker | scrabble | bridge     |

