.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, 7up, fanta
There 4 different types of food: carrot, peas, pepper, papaya
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person eating carrot##7
5. the person eating peas is somewhere between the person eating pepper and the person drinking cola##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Beverage           | cola | fanta | 7up | mirinda  |
| Food   | carrot     | peas   | pepper    | papaya |

