.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, july, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, snowboarding, basketball
1. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in august##7
2. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is basketball##2
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Birthday    | august   | january  | may  | july |
| Sport   | skateboarding | snowboarding | parkour | basketball    |

