.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, drawing, traveling
House: cottage, victorian, ranch-style, gothic-revival
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the victorian house##6
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
5. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the victorian house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby           | hiking | drawing  | magic-tricks  | traveling |
| House   | cottage  | gothic-revival | victorian | ranch-style   |

