.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, august, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, skateboarding, basketball
1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's birthday is in april##7
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Birthday         | april    | august | july     | december |
| Sport   | skateboarding | basketball  | rugby | lacrosse |

 